metadata.name: Azure Cartographical Story
metadata.description:
A map is a tool and a guide to find your way to where you want to go next.  Full of possibilities to help you find the next place and unpack the world with a little help.  Unless you're the cartographer in which case they show where you've been, where you've blazed a path.  

Sometimes you just need them to get back home if you've lost your way...
